<paragraph blockId="161.[151,1437,726,1833]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,216,1519,1545]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Note:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Pavesi, 1884" authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[226,656,1519,1545]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">
<emphasis box="[226,501,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis erinacei</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Pavesi, P." box="[510,656,1519,1545]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="446 - 486" refId="ref236960" refString="Pavesi, P. (1884) Spedizione italiana nell'Africa equatoriale; resultati zoologici. Aracnidi del regno di Scioa. Materiali per lo studio della fauna tunisina raccolti da G. ed L. Doria. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova (1883 - 1884), 20, 446 - 486." type="journal article" year="1884">Pavesi, 1884</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
has priority over 
<taxonomicName authority="Feldman-Musham, 1951" authorityName="Feldman-Musham" authorityYear="1951" box="[867,1431,1518,1545]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">
<emphasis box="[867,1141,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis erinacei</emphasis>
Feldman-Musham, 1951
</taxonomicName>
, which is a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Pavesi, 1884" authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[426,859,1555,1581]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">
<emphasis box="[426,700,1555,1581]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis erinacei</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Pavesi, P." box="[710,859,1555,1581]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="446 - 486" refId="ref236960" refString="Pavesi, P. (1884) Spedizione italiana nell'Africa equatoriale; resultati zoologici. Aracnidi del regno di Scioa. Materiali per lo studio della fauna tunisina raccolti da G. ed L. Doria. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova (1883 - 1884), 20, 446 - 486." type="journal article" year="1884">Pavesi, 1884</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. The female of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[1045,1319,1555,1581]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">
<emphasis box="[1045,1319,1555,1581]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis erinacei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pavesi, P." box="[187,343,1591,1617]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="446 - 486" refId="ref236960" refString="Pavesi, P. (1884) Spedizione italiana nell'Africa equatoriale; resultati zoologici. Aracnidi del regno di Scioa. Materiali per lo studio della fauna tunisina raccolti da G. ed L. Doria. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova (1883 - 1884), 20, 446 - 486." type="journal article" year="1884">Pavesi (1884)</bibRefCitation>
does not belong to 
<taxonomicName box="[567,740,1591,1617]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[567,740,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as explained in 
<bibRefCitation author="Feldman-Muhsam, B." box="[933,1224,1590,1617]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="372 - 378" refId="ref199813" refString="Feldman-Muhsam, B. (1953) On the identity of Haemaphysalis erinacei and H. taurica. Bulletin of the Research Council of Israel, 2, 372 - 378." type="journal article" year="1953">Feldman-Muhsam (1953)</bibRefCitation>
; therefore, translations of the description of the female of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[606,879,1627,1653]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">
<emphasis box="[606,879,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis erinacei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pavesi, P." box="[922,1079,1627,1653]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="446 - 486" refId="ref236960" refString="Pavesi, P. (1884) Spedizione italiana nell'Africa equatoriale; resultati zoologici. Aracnidi del regno di Scioa. Materiali per lo studio della fauna tunisina raccolti da G. ed L. Doria. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova (1883 - 1884), 20, 446 - 486." type="journal article" year="1884">Pavesi (1884)</bibRefCitation>
, as in 
<bibRefCitation author="Neumann, L. G." box="[1153,1346,1627,1653]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="324 - 420" refId="ref233279" refString="Neumann, L. G. (1897) Revision de la famille des ixodides (2 e memoire). Memoires de la Societe Zoologique de France, 10, 324 - 420." type="journal article" year="1897">
<taxonomicName authority="Guglielmone &amp; Petney &amp; Robbins, 2020" authorityName="Guglielmone &amp; Petney &amp; Robbins" authorityYear="2020" box="[1153,1262,1627,1653]" pageId="161" pageNumber="289" rank="subGenus" status="subgen. n." subGenus="Neumann">Neumann</taxonomicName>
(1897)
</bibRefCitation>
, are not included in the above lists. There are also several redescriptions of subspecies of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[1072,1345,1663,1689]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">
<emphasis box="[1072,1345,1663,1689]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis erinacei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
that are not included in our lists. Morphological and molecular differences among populations, as described in 
<bibRefCitation author="Filippova, N. A. &amp; Panova, I. V. &amp; Musatov, S. A." pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="193 - 215" refId="ref201998" refString="Filippova, N. A., Panova, I. V. &amp; Musatov, S. A. (1993) The taxonomic pattern of the polytypic species Haemaphysalis erinacei (Ixodidae). Parazitologiya, 27, 193 - 215. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1993">
Filippova 
<emphasis box="[151,209,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">et al.</emphasis>
(1993)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Filippova, N. A." box="[308,498,1735,1761]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" refId="ref200812" refString="Filippova, N. A. (1997) Ixodid ticks of the subfamily Amblyomminae. In: Fauna of Russia and neighbouring countries, 4 (5) Nauka, St. Petersburg, 436 pp. [in Russian]" type="book" year="1997">Filippova (1997)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Hornok, S. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Otranto, D. &amp; Keskin, A. &amp; Lia, R. P. &amp; Konnstchan, J. &amp; Takacs, N. &amp; Farkas, R. &amp; Sandor, A. D." box="[556,806,1735,1762]" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" pagination="1 - 7" refId="ref214650" refString="Hornok, S., Wang, Y., Otranto, D., Keskin, A., Lia, R. P., Konnstchan, J., Takacs, N., Farkas, R. &amp; Sandor, A. D. (2016 c) Phylogenetic analysis of Haemaphysalis erinacei Pavesi, 1884 (Acarina: Ixodidae) from China, Turkey, Italy and Romania. Parasites &amp; Vectors, 9 (article 643), 1 - 7. https: // doi. org / 10.1186 / s 13071 - 016 - 1927 - 1" type="journal article" year="2016">
Hornok 
<emphasis box="[650,708,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">et al.</emphasis>
(2016c)
</bibRefCitation>
, are strong indicators that more than one taxon may be represented under the name 
<emphasis box="[469,748,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[469,744,1771,1797]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">Haemaphysalis erinacei</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[755,795,1771,1797]" country="South Sudan" name="Lakes" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">See</collectingRegion>
also 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bedford" authorityYear="1929" box="[856,1117,1771,1797]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cooleyi">
<emphasis box="[856,1117,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis cooleyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoogstraal" authorityYear="1972" box="[1172,1436,1771,1797]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pedetes">
<emphasis box="[1172,1436,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Haemaphysalis pedetes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for their confusion with 
<emphasis box="[423,702,1807,1833]" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pavesi" authorityYear="1884" box="[423,698,1807,1833]" class="Arachnida" family="Ixodidae" genus="Haemaphysalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ixodida" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erinacei">Haemaphysalis erinacei</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
